        "pitch_and_presentation": 7
    },

    "final_verdict": "FireBI demonstrates good potential but requires significant refinement to become a competitive solution. Recommendations: 1) Develop more proprietary technology to reduce third-party dependencies, 2) Focus on a specific industry vertical to create clearer differentiation, 3) Strengthen security and compliance measures, 4) Provide concrete demonstrations and performance metrics, 5) Create a more detailed technical architecture documentation. The project scores above average overall (6.25/10) but has room for improvement, particularly in innovation and technical depth."
